\[OpenCurlyQuote]d\[CloseCurlyQuote] in Bogoliubov fully-contracted terms are \
involute. For their numeric counterpart, the following convention is adopted: \
\nIndex > 0 \[DoubleRightArrow] ",
 StyleBox["standard",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 "\nIndex < 0 \[DoubleRightArrow] ",
 StyleBox["involute",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 "."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8874623260617843`*^9, 3.8874623745747523`*^9}, {
  3.88746257423927*^9, 3.887462578566905*^9}, {3.888312600987131*^9, 
  3.8883126358497353`*^9}, {3.91129488637901*^9, 
  3.911295044011321*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"c4873010-64a5-415a-aa6e-\
57dcb0b583ed"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Selection of the Nambu component of the one-body potential", "Section",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.912081665987741*^9, 
  3.9120817133455973`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"051f5b5a-48df-4cb9-93f5-\
dbcc0d763658"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "The analytical results presented henceforth refer to an element of the \
product between ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"U", "(", 
    SubscriptBox["t", "2"]}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "7242ecf8-5d32-47fa-9873-2dcb3990f405"],
 "), ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"U", "(", 
    SubscriptBox["t", "3"]}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "85aefea0-40cd-4300-821c-b23e6a0b8433"],
 ") and the second-quantization operators with external single-particle \
indices. At second order, such elements are specified by the two pairs of  \
Nambu indices that determine the component ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox[
    SubscriptBox["u", "ef"], 
    RowBox[{
     SubscriptBox["g", "5"], 
     SubscriptBox["g", "6"]}]], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "4ad3c726-6ba6-497f-908a-d43cc95ede3e"],
 " (",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox[
    SubscriptBox["u", "gh"], 
    RowBox[{
     SubscriptBox["g", "7"], 
     SubscriptBox["g", "8"]}]], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "6d487157-3f43-4f47-9431-3f0e9aae692d"],
 ") of the auxiliary one-body potential ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"U", "(", 
    SubscriptBox["t", "2"]}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "6a6eca38-068d-43ab-9fa9-8b909d688b84"],
 ") (",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"U", "(", 
    SubscriptBox["t", "3"]}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "32799df0-3544-47a7-b748-4529d33a5860"],
 ")). The indices are stored as { ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["g", "5"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "0eab68a4-6ed5-445c-b5a8-7e9056be5f7d"],
 ", ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["g", "6"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "4822ae4c-dd00-4317-9217-a905032183f7"],
 ",",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{" ", 
    SubscriptBox["g", "7"]}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "d10f5538-01bc-4bd4-9050-2da95151cd5b"],
 ", ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["g", "8"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "d26ee7ab-ee8d-4787-89aa-41104decc327"],
 "} in the array \[OpenCurlyQuote]UNambu\[CloseCurlyQuote], together with the \
associated multiplicity arising from the product between ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"U", "(", 
    SubscriptBox["t", "2"]}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "73e70ee5-d4d3-4be1-903a-7655a5d6efa8"],
 ") and ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"U", "(", 
    SubscriptBox["t", "3"]}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "fb01ae7a-4cb7-4918-b8a8-691f0c11b09b"],
 "). Since the single-particle indices are summed, the products ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox[
    SubscriptBox["u", "ef"], "12"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "0b09361e-e276-4ac3-8396-03249c5dfca3"],
 " ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox[
    SubscriptBox["u", "gh"], "21"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "e4ba07a2-e491-4ddb-8ff3-38ce0ca4e977"],
 " and ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox[
    SubscriptBox["u", "ef"], "21"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "e47af00e-4575-48b9-b087-1299720c0b04"],
 " ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox[
    SubscriptBox["u", "gh"], "12"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "bd22683e-16cf-4353-aefd-a9813d7caf76"],
 " give rise to identical contributions, hence are summed together, resulting \
in a multiplicity equal to 2. The same occurs for all other contributions \
with ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["g", "5"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "34765731-bc00-40ec-bfbe-52bfdc80e521"],
 " \[NotEqual] ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    SubscriptBox["g", "7"], " "}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "3ae4d96a-0288-4c64-8d2d-376170f3faf6"],
 "and/or ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["g", "6"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "6657d59f-eaf1-4b6d-8f2e-6dc974741f67"],
 "\[NotEqual] ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["g", "8"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "3caf48fe-1966-4aef-a609-878e57bf8a8c"],
 ". As a result,  the component ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox[
    SubscriptBox["u", "ef"], "11"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "a450da72-de83-4b13-a26a-0988ded20db2"],
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox[
    SubscriptBox["u", "gh"], "11"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "f9245797-da16-44e9-a33f-d86c0fa11b1e"],
 " and is encoded by \[OpenCurlyQuote]UNambu[[1]]\[CloseCurlyQuote] , ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox[
    SubscriptBox["u", "ef"], "12"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "9433ce88-5392-4b19-b00c-de878df5bb90"],
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox[
    SubscriptBox["u", "gh"], "12"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "9061a594-4b9f-40be-8b06-518695ac8cf2"],
 "  is mapped to \[OpenCurlyQuote]UNambu[[2]]\[CloseCurlyQuote], ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox[
    SubscriptBox["u", "ef"], "21"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "8da3ef8b-5b0c-40a4-b3d4-fdb3089bb10b"],
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox[
    SubscriptBox["u", "gh"], "21"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "4edc7cea-f7a0-4130-b17d-91925935745b"],
 " to \[OpenCurlyQuote]UNambu[[3]]\[CloseCurlyQuote] and ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox[
    SubscriptBox["u", "ef"], "22"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "effc6299-bbff-4285-96ee-3eaa61b3a386"],
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox[
    SubscriptBox["u", "ef"], "22"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "363355d9-91c3-472a-8d8d-ff2eb0d74860"],
 "  to \[OpenCurlyQuote]UNambu[[4]]\[CloseCurlyQuote] and are associated with \
multiplicity 1. Analogously,  the component ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox[
    SubscriptBox["u", "ef"], "11"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "bc0ab5cf-0d82-474b-ad00-ebbcb9b8fcff"],
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox[
    SubscriptBox["u", "gh"], "12"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "4d946181-b6dd-4074-81db-0eb20c374934"],
 " and is encoded by \[OpenCurlyQuote]UNambu[[5]]\[CloseCurlyQuote]",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{",", " ", 
    RowBox[{
     FormBox[
      SuperscriptBox[
       SubscriptBox["u", "ef"], "11"],
      TraditionalForm], 
     SuperscriptBox[
      SubscriptBox["u", "gh"], "21"]}]}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "16fda42e-20a4-4822-a685-23632ece8325"],
 " is mapped to \[OpenCurlyQuote]UNambu[[6]]\[CloseCurlyQuote],  ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{" ", 
    RowBox[{
     FormBox[
      SuperscriptBox[
       SubscriptBox["u", "ef"], "11"],
      TraditionalForm], 
     SuperscriptBox[
      SubscriptBox["u", "gh"], "22"]}]}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "a4a01449-c0a4-4ca3-933a-923eec09d018"],
 " to \[OpenCurlyQuote]UNambu[[7]]\[CloseCurlyQuote], ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    SuperscriptBox[
     SubscriptBox["u", "ef"], "12"], 
    SuperscriptBox[
     SubscriptBox["u", "gh"], "21"]}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "3ba23741-8228-472d-8981-6f525bf9ada0"],
 " to \[OpenCurlyQuote]UNambu[[8]]\[CloseCurlyQuote], ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    SuperscriptBox[
     SubscriptBox["u", "ef"], "12"], 
    SuperscriptBox[
     SubscriptBox["u", "gh"], "22"]}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "afee3da5-7106-4340-afed-3f2a9c9aaa30"],
 " to \[OpenCurlyQuote]UNambu[[9]]\[CloseCurlyQuote] and ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    SuperscriptBox[
     SubscriptBox["u", "ef"], "21"], 
    SuperscriptBox[
     SubscriptBox["u", "gh"], "22"]}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "26d85c38-35c3-4cd6-ae6e-d5c63146628f"],
 " to \[OpenCurlyQuote]UNambu[[10]]\[CloseCurlyQuote]."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.912081776386461*^9, 3.9120818052616024`*^9}, {
  3.912081937013556*^9, 3.912082002664327*^9}, {3.912082104513921*^9, 
